  <description><![CDATA[<p>If you are looking for the confidence of a high altitude, snow-sure resort, on one of the world’s <em>Top Ten</em> ski areas, with the convenience of skiing to and from your own ski room door, then you have come to the right place. And if you want all those plus-points combined with outstanding value for money, great food, wine included with dinner and the warmest and friendliest of welcomes, then look no further – our popular Chalet Hotel St. Christoph is for you.</p>
<p>The location is simply unbeatable. The Maiensee button lift starts just outside the ski room door, or take the 2-minute walk to the St. Christophbahn covered quad chairlift, which takes you straight up into the heart of the <a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St. Anton</a> side of the mighty <a data-udi="umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2}" title="Arlberg Ski Area">Arlberg ski area</a>. If you fancy the spectacular slopes of <a data-udi="umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6}" title="Lech">Lech</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/754fd3eb2ae94fa89ed0dfc04d2b29b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/754fd3eb2ae94fa89ed0dfc04d2b29b6}" title="Zurs">Zürs</a> for a change, and the wonderful ‘White Ring’ circuit for a great day out, the ski bus stops 50m from the hotel. Beginners and families are downright spoiled, with the ski school meeting place and nursery slopes immediately alongside the hotel.</p>
<p>The comfortable facilities on offer inside the Chalet Hotel start with a welcoming lobby and reception area, connecting through to the excellent value residents-only bar and comfy lounge. The attractive dining room sets the scene for our Chalet Hotel dining, and there are sauna and a large indoor swimming pool with mountain views and relaxing loungers on which to unwind after a great day’s skiing. Well-appointed bedrooms, many with interconnecting doors, complete the picture for a thoroughly comfortable stay.</p>
<p><em>"What a fantastic week we had in Austria! We truly had the best time and were so well looked after, I was genuinely impressed with the whole Inghams experience and all the staff went out of their way to make us feel welcome." </em><strong><em>- Mrs Mandel, April 2019</em></strong></p>
<p><em><strong>"</strong>Great having ski school next door and ski hire in the same building."</em> <strong><em>- Ms Rowen, March 2019</em></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: right;"> </p>]]></description>
