  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Superb ski-in/ski-out location, with ski lift and ski school meeting place on the doorstep</li>
<li>Snow-sure location at 1,800m on the massive Arlberg ski area</li>
<li>Maiensee T-bar lift just short distance from the ski room door</li>
<li>Heated indoor swimming pool open all day and sauna from 4 pm, towels provided by the pool </li>
<li>Comfortable residents’ bar, separate lounge and evening Mogul bar</li>
<li>An attractive and spacious dining room</li>
<li>Comfortable bedrooms, all with private en-suite shower/WC, TV, safe and hairdryer, and many with balcony</li>
<li>Interconnecting rooms available, ideal for families</li>
<li>Ski rental and servicing, within the hotel, open Fri afternoon, Sat and Sun</li>
<li>Ski bus for St Anton/Lech/Zürs stops 50m from the hotel</li>
<li>Table tennis table, pool table and a couple of games machines in the winter gardens </li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
