  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Lower Ground Floor:</strong> Ski rental service, Ski &amp; Boot room with heated boot racks, door to slopes.</li>
<li><strong>Ground Floor:</strong> Reception, residents-exclusive bar; sports bar with live sports; two open-plan lounge areas, one with log fire attractive dining-room. Lift to 3rd floor.</li>
<li><strong>1st Floor:</strong><br />Indoor swimming pool, sauna &amp; relaxation area with loungers; children’s playroom.<br />Room 101 - Double with shower/wc/balcony<br />Rooms 103, 105, 106, 107 &amp; 108 - Twins with shower/wc/balcony<br />Room 104 - Single room with shower/wc/balcony<br />Rooms 109, 111, 112, 114, 115, 116, 118, 119, 120, 122 &amp; 123 - Twins with shower/wc<br />Rooms 110 &amp; 117 - Single room with shower/wc <br />Room 121 - Double with shower/wc</li>
<li><strong>2nd Floor:</strong><br />Room 201 - Double with shower/wc/balcony<br />Rooms 202, 203, 205, 206, 207 &amp; 208 - Twins with shower/wc/balcony<br />Room 204 - Single room with shower/wc/balcony<br />Rooms 209, 211, 212, 214, 215, 216, 218, 219, 220, 222 &amp; 223 - Twins with shower/wc<br />Rooms 210 &amp; 217 - Single room with shower/wc<br />Room 221 - Double with shower/wc</li>
<li><strong>3rd Floor:</strong><br />Room 301 - Double with shower/wc/balcony<br />Rooms 302, 303, 305, 306, 307 &amp; 308 - Twins with shower/WC/balcony<br />Room 304 - Single room with shower/wc/balcony. <br />Rooms 309, 311, 312, 314, 315, 316, 318, 319, 320, 322 &amp; 323 - Twins with shower/WC<br />Rooms 310 &amp; 317 - Single room with shower/WC<br />Room 321 - Double with shower/WC</li>
<li><strong>4th Floor:</strong><br />Room 401 - Double with shower/WC (under eaves)<br />Rooms 402, 403, 405, 406, 407 &amp; 408 - Twins with shower/WC (under the eaves)<br />Room 404 - Single room with shower/WC (under the eaves)</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>2nd Floor Winter Garden*: (For Winter 20/21) </strong><br />Rooms 510, 511, 512, 515 &amp; 516 - Twins with bath/WC<br />Rooms 514 &amp; 517 - Double with bath/WC</li>
</ul>
<p>*Winter Garden rooms are of a 3.5* standard and there is no lift access to these rooms</p>
<p>All rooms have Sat-TV, safe, hairdryer and toiletries provided. Rooms are cleaned on Saturdays and mid-week with an optional request for a towel change.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
